	<entry>
		<title>Poem On Prayer</title>
		<link href="https://yjdx.netlify.app/yjdx/blog/prayer/"/>
		<updated>2023-12-04T00:00:00Z</updated>
		<id>https://yjdx.netlify.app/yjdx/blog/prayer/</id>
		<content type="html">&lt;h3 id=&quot;poem-on-prayer&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot;&gt;Poem On Prayer &lt;a class=&quot;header-anchor&quot; href=&quot;https://yjdx.netlify.app/yjdx/blog/prayer/&quot;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Prayer&lt;/strong&gt;, What a &lt;em&gt;beautiful&lt;/em&gt; thing&lt;br&gt;
Raid the &lt;strong&gt;devil&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;em&gt;victory&lt;/em&gt; you shall bring;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Abandon&lt;/em&gt; your &lt;strong&gt;wordly addictions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Yearn&lt;/em&gt; for &lt;strong&gt;God&lt;/strong&gt;,&lt;br&gt;
He will &lt;em&gt;eradicate&lt;/em&gt; your &lt;strong&gt;afflictions&lt;/strong&gt;;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Raise&lt;/em&gt; up your problems,&lt;br&gt;
&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Prayer helps with that&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Faithfulness&lt;/strong&gt;, it &lt;em&gt;instills&lt;/em&gt; in you,&lt;br&gt;
Certainly &lt;strong&gt;not&lt;/strong&gt; the spirit of a &lt;em&gt;brat.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;~Yeshua D&#39;Costa&lt;/p&gt;
</content>
